Bch Kinh Xy Confessions
========1 pht======

HOT NEWS: Trung Quc ang x l lin tc 8 ting v sng Hng.

Sng nay, Ban Ngoi v tnh Vn Nam, Trung Quc bt ng thng bo cho Vit Nam v vic pha Trung Quc x l trn sng Hng. Thi gian x l l 8 ting, t 9h n 17h ngy hm nay. Tuy nhin, pha Trung Quc ch thng bo m khng cung cp thng tin c th v lu lng x l. Hnh ng khng xanh chn ny s gy rt nhiu kh khn cho Vit Nam trong vic ng ph l. Trong hon cnh nc trn sng Hng on c...hy qua thnh ph Lo Cai vn mc cao, nguy c l chng l l rt ln.

Vic thng bo x l t nh my thy in M Sn xung sng Hng l cha tng c tin l trong lch s. Nhng ngy va qua, tnh hnh ma bo khin Trung Quc ang hng chu cc trn hng thy trm nm c mt. Ngi dn ti nhiu thnh ph Trung Quc vn ang t chc ua thuyn, lt sng, bt c trn ng ph.

Ban ch o Trung ng v phng chng thin tai c cng in khn gi cc tnh, thnh ph Lo Cai, Yn Bi, Ph Th, Vnh Phc v H Ni, yu cu khn trng ng ph trc thng tin thy in M Sn x l xung sng Hng. T ngy 17/8 n nay, tnh hnh ma l min ni pha Bc rt cng thng khi c 7 ngi cht, 4 ngi b thng. Hn 1.000 nh dn b h hng hoc di di khn cp.

Mi ngi sng lu vc sng Hng cn ht sc cn trng!!

Theo: NLD
Via: #Beatvn
